        <briefdescription>
<para>Compute per-link poses from generalized positions. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Computes articulated link transforms from generalized positions.</para>
<para>Performs a kinematic traversal from root to leaves to assemble: joint transforms, parent-relative transforms, and world transforms for each link in the articulation.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">model</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para><ref refid="structnovaphy_1_1_articulation" kindref="compound">Articulation</ref> graph and joint definitions. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">q</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Generalized position vector, length = model.total_q(). </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="out">X_J</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Joint-motion transforms, one per link. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="out">X_up</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Parent-to-child spatial transforms, one per link. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="out">X_world</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>World-frame rigid transforms (position + quaternion), one per link. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>void</para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>Output transforms are expressed in world coordinates for rendering and downstream dynamics calls. </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="warning"><para>Input dimensions must match model topology.</para>
</simplesect>
<parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">model</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para><ref refid="structnovaphy_1_1_articulation" kindref="compound">Articulation</ref> model containing joint tree topology. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">q</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Generalized coordinates. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="out">X_J</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Per-link joint transforms. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="out">X_up</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Per-link parent transforms in spatial form. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="out">X_world</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Per-link world transforms for visualization/queries. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
