        <briefdescription>
<para>Compute generalized forces using RNEA (inverse dynamics). </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Computes inverse dynamics using recursive Newton-Euler passes.</para>
<para>Recursive Newton-Euler Algorithm evaluates the joint efforts required to realize a prescribed motion state (q, qd, qdd), optionally including external link forces.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">model</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para><ref refid="structnovaphy_1_1_articulation" kindref="compound">Articulation</ref> graph and inertial properties. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">q</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Generalized positions. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">qd</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Generalized velocities. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">qdd</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Generalized accelerations. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">gravity</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Gravity vector in world frame (m/s^2). </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">f_ext</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Optional external spatial forces per link in link-local frame (N, N*m). </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>Generalized force vector tau (joint torques/forces in SI units).</para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>Time complexity is O(n) for n links. </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="warning"><para>If provided, f_ext must contain one entry per link.</para>
</simplesect>
