        <detaileddescription>
<para>Computes the articulated mass matrix using CRBA.</para>
<para>Composite Rigid Body Algorithm computes H(q), the configuration- dependent mass matrix used in forward dynamics and model-based control.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
