    <briefdescription>
<para>Featherstone-family rigid-body dynamics algorithms. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This namespace provides forward kinematics, inverse dynamics (RNEA), mass-matrix assembly (CRBA), and forward dynamics for a single tree-structured articulation.</para>
<para>Spatial-vector convention is [angular; linear], and computations follow standard rigid-body dynamics in SI units (m, kg, s, N, rad). </para>
    </detaileddescription>
